Package supervisor.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveUI
    The view that is shown on a supervisor that is active - consists of information about the election, and a grid of all of the machines on the network.
    AMachineView
    Abstract panel for a machine view, that contains an update method
    BallotScannerMachineView
    This class is the machine tile view of the Ballot Scanner when it is on the network.
    InactiveUI
    The view that is shown on an inactive supervisor - only shows the number of machines connected and an Activate button.
    MachineViewGenerator
    The MachineViewGenerator is a sort of "cache" that only allows you to create one instance of a view for a machine's model (assuming that all views are created through the same MVG).
    MyJButton
    A decorator for a JButton that uses a standardized font, and turns on antialiasing.
    MyJLabel
    A decorator for a JLabel that uses a standardized font, and turns on antialiasing.
    OverrideDialog
    A dialog that is shown when the poll worker attempts to override an authorization.
    SupervisorMachineView
    The view for a supervisor on the network.
    TallyDialog Deprecated
    replaced with TallyResultsFrame
    TallyResultsFrame
    Created with IntelliJ IDEA.
    TapView
    This is a Tap ribbon that is placed in the left panel of the Supervisor's ActiveUI and represents whether or not the Tap is responsive and on the network.
    View
    The Supervisor's view.
    VoteBoxBoothView
    The view of a VoteBox booth on the network.
